				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Glad you liked it. I never imagined the feathers would be understood as prosaically as from a collection nearby<br />
See what you mean with &#8216;down&#8217; &#8211; will look for a suitable (more technical) replacement.<br />
&#8216;tried to&#8217; &#8211; Yes! Sometimes you look at your own work and wonder what the hell you where thinking.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

