				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>I found this piece very beautiful and serene (even with feathers strewn about the room :-)) I completely read it as the mother slowly drifting into another form/life as a bird &#8211; becoming something else as she died. It is a lovely and very positive death scene. </p>
<p>I loved the flowing descriptions of avian dreams and wished for more of them.</p>
<p>I work with commas similarly to docinatrix &#8211; by feel rather than a set of rules. I had the same problems with the same sentences.</p>
<p>Thanks <img src="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-includes/images/smilies/simple-smile.png" alt=":-)" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p>
